questionText:
Voici un extrait de configuration iOS pour un widget panier. Que manque-t-il ?
```json
{
  "expo": {
    "ios": {
      "widgets": [
        {
          "name": "CartWidget",
          "description": "Affiche le nombre d'articles dans le panier"
        }
      ]
    }
  }
}
```

options:
```json
"android": {
  "quickActions": [
    { "name": "Panier", "icon": "shopping_cart", "url": "myapp://cart" }
  ]
}
```

```json
"android": {
  "shortcuts": [
    { "shortcutId": "cart", "title": "Panier", "icon": "shopping_cart" }
  ]
}
```

```json
"android": {
  "intentFilters": [
    { "action": "VIEW_CART", "data": "myapp://cart" }
  ]
}
```

```json
"android": {
  "appShortcuts": {
    "static": [ { "id": "cart", "label": "Panier" } ]
  }
}
```
